          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
              <div class="bg-teal-50 w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6"><svg class="w-8 h-8 text-teal-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" /></svg></div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Devis Gratuit, Sans Engagement</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Chaque demande reçoit une proposition personnalisée, gratuite et sans engagement. Réponse garantie sous 48h ouvrées.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
              <div class="bg-teal-50 w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6"><svg class="w-8 h-8 text-teal-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z" /></svg></div>
